{
  "texts": [
    "We believe that an LLM-based orchestrator could be beneficial in XAI for clinical settings as it could provide a verbalization of explanations adapted to the current user and situation.",
    "Moreover, LLM-based technologies could enable a bidirectional \"dialogue\" between users and (X)AI systems.",
    "In the more or less distant future, such systems may serve as a virtual assistant capable of working as a counselor in clinical scenarios.",
    "Properties From a clinical point of view, we propose the following attributes for the XAI orchestrator to be helpful in daily practice (Table 2): 1.",
    "The XAI orchestrator must cope with a varying set of potentially sparse input data."
  ]
}